    "body": "We're not quite there on the entity implementation path. But here is some info for when we do it.\r\n1. listen on use_entity packet\r\n2. send entity_state with status = 18\r\n3. when mating is done, do `entity.sendMetadata([{\"key\":12,\"type\":0,\"value\": 1}]);` to stop \"love mode\"\r\n\r\nalso see http://sprunge.us/NGVN to see a dump of doing that on vanilla. ",
